e. If the duergar lacks the room to become Large, it attains the maximum size possible in the space available.\", \"special\": null},{\"name\": \"Invisibility\", \"bonus\": null, \"damage\": \"<strong>Invisibility.</strong> The duergar magically turns invisible until it attacks, casts a spell, or uses its Enlarge, or until its concentration is broken, up to 1 hour (as if concentrating on a spell). Any equipment the duergar wears or carries is invisible with it .\", \"special\": null}]','Duergar.jpg',1,972);
